<sect1>
	<title>Accessing the Program</title>
<para>
Gpe-Play-Memo is accessable in the utilities folder. To access it tap on the play memo icon.
<figure>
	<title>GPE Utilities Folder</title>
<mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="utilitiesfolder.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject>
</figure>
<figure>
	<title>Main Application Screen</title>
<mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="mainappscreen.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject>
</figure>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1>
	<title>Using the Application</title>
<para>
Select the memo file to play by tapping on it and then tap on the ok button.
</para>
<figure>
	<title>Playing in Action</title>
<mediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="playmemo.png" format="PNG"/></imageobject></mediaobject>
</figure>
</sect1>
